  LeftSpeaker:
  - {fileID: 1028370226, guid: 954a5168c9e339142be33458ba765729, type: 3}
  RightSpeaker:
  - {fileID: 7346647256224613308, guid: 60a07cc2ecd17e94e9043714da41d6d8, type: 3}
  - {fileID: -4514844369508590888, guid: 60a07cc2ecd17e94e9043714da41d6d8, type: 3}
  text:
  - Hello!
  - Huh? What?
  - Hi! I was flying by when I saw your crystal. May I have it?
  - What? outside? what do you mean??
  - 'Y''know. outside. not space, technically, more ... void? i guess. '
  - Theres like whole worlds out here.
  - What?
  - Worlds?
  - This is all there is.
  - Just me, and my house.
  - And then you just ... appear? how did you just appear here?
  - Oh, I just no-clipped in by moving backwards.
  - I... do not understand...
  - So anyways, can I have your crystal?
  - 'I... '
  - I'll take that as a yes. Thank you!
  textMetadata:
  - L,0
  - R,0
  - L,0
  - R,0
  - L,0
  - L,0
